HEADWORD: Declaratively
<hw>De*clar"a*tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>By distinct assertion;
not impliedly; in the form of a declaration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The priest shall expiate it, that is,
<qex>declaratively</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Bates.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

